data.description: Enjoy Your Morning Coffee On Your South-facing Front Porch Equipped With A Retractable Awning! This Peaceful Neighborhood Is Conveniently Located Near Shopping Centers And Schools. You're Also Within Proximity To The Chesapeake Bay And A Straightforward Drive To The Oceanfront. There's An Abundance Of Local Activities Such As Fishing, Kayaking, & Biking! The Property Includes A Generously Sized Detached Garage, A 3 Year Old Roof, A 4 Year Old HVAC System, Stainless Steel Appliances, And Many Newer Windows! This Home Boasts A Bonus Room That Can Serve As An Office, Den, Or Extra Bedroom. The Oversized Garage Is Well-equipped With Power Supply & An Overhead I-beam With A Pulley System (Perfect For Mechanics!). Ample Street Parking Is Available, Along With The Privacy Of A Fenced Yard. Come Visit And Discover Why So Many Residents In This Community End Up Calling It Home!
